            <title>[HBASE-1807] KeyFilter for filtering based on comparsions of row, column, and qualifiers of KeyValues</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1807</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;From: Angus He up on hbase-user:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Subject: Is there any ways to retrieve values whose columns match specific regular expression?&lt;br/&gt;
Is this functionality available in the current implementation? If not, is there any plans on this?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See attached patch. Low impact change, can go into 0.20.0. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
